OL,3,CPeace, Love...and an Honorary Degree
OL,4,Cfor Ringo Starr
OL,6,FBeatles drummer Ringo Starr has been
OL,7,Fawarded an honorary doctorate by the
OL,8,FUniversity of Liverpool on his 86th
OL,9,Fbirthday.
OL,11,FThe musician, born Richard Starkey in
OL,12,FLiverpool's Dingle district, received
OL,13,Fthe Honorary Doctor of Music during a
OL,14,Fprivate ceremony at Beverly Hills Park
OL,15,Fin Los Angeles, ahead of his birthday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
