OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1783676987
OL,3,CPeace, Love...and an Honorary Degree
OL,4,Cfor Ringo Starr
OL,6,FUniversity Chancellor Wendy
OL,7,FBeetlestone travelled to California to
OL,8,Fpresent the award, praising Starr's
OL,9,Fcontribution to music and the way he
OL,10,Fhas helped shape Liverpool's identity
OL,11,Fand worldwide reputation.
OL,13,FAccepting the honour, Starr thanked
OL,14,Fthe university for making the journey
OL,15,Fto present the degree and reflected on
OL,16,Fhis Liverpool roots.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
