PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1783676987
OL,3,CPeace, Love...and an Honorary Degree
OL,4,Cfor Ringo Starr
OL,6,FHe encouraged this year's graduates to
OL,7,Ffollow their dreams, recalling how his
OL,8,Ffamily had initially discouraged him
OL,9,Ffrom pursuing a career as a full-time
OL,10,Fdrummer.
OL,12,F"It all worked out," he said.
OL,14,FHe added: "I want to thank the
OL,15,FUniversity of Liverpool for this
OL,16,FHonorary Degree and for coming all the
OL,17,Fway to LA to bestow it. I'm really
OL,18,Fhonoured.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@TO]vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
