CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1783676987
OL,3,CPeace, Love...and an Honorary Degree
OL,4,Cfor Ringo Starr
OL,6,F"Today is my birthday, and as everyone
OL,7,Fknows, I was born in Liverpool. It is
OL,8,Fmy hometown and I'll always love it.
OL,10,F"I've been thinking back on my life a
OL,11,Flot lately ` and when I chose to
OL,12,Fbecome a drummer full time ` my family
OL,13,Fdiscouraged me.
OL,15,F"And they could have been right! But
OL,16,Fthey weren't ` it all worked out.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
