OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1783676987
OL,3,CPeace, Love...and an Honorary Degree
OL,4,Cfor Ringo Starr
OL,6,F"So to all the graduates back in
OL,7,FLiverpool ` I send Peace & Love and
OL,8,Fwant to say don't be afraid to follow
OL,9,Fyour dreams ` or take that right turn
OL,10,Fand see where it goes.... it could
OL,11,Flead to an Honorary Doctorate from the
OL,12,FUniversity of Liverpool."
OL,14,FStarr rose to global fame as the
OL,15,Fdrummer with The Beatles, the band
OL,16,Fthat transformed popular music after
OL,17,Fforming in Liverpool in the early
OL,18,F1960s.
OL,26,@tD@YO]
