PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1783676987
OL,3,CPeace, Love...and an Honorary Degree
OL,4,Cfor Ringo Starr
OL,6,FAlongside a successful solo career
OL,7,Fspanning more than five decades, he
OL,8,Fhas remained an ambassador for his
OL,9,Fhome city and is well known for
OL,10,Fpromoting his message of "peace and
OL,11,Flove".
OL,13,FThe University of Liverpool said the
OL,14,Fhonorary degree recognised Starr's
OL,15,Foutstanding contribution to music,
OL,16,Fculture and Liverpool's international
OL,17,Freputation.
OL,26,@rD@ZOUsD@EO]
