OL,3,CPeace, Love...and an Honorary Degree
OL,4,Cfor Ringo Starr
OL,6,FUniversity of Liverpool Vice-
OL,7,FChancellor, Professor Tim Jones, said:
OL,8,F"The University of Liverpool is a
OL,9,Frenowned authority on the academic
OL,10,Fstudy of The Beatles and this honorary
OL,11,Fdegree expresses our sincere respect
OL,12,Ffor the contribution Ringo has made to
OL,13,Fmusic and to Liverpool's heritage and
OL,14,Fculture. I'm delighted to welcome him
OL,15,Finto the university community."
